{"tid":2321864,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【#甲足澳門盃】賓菲加23:1大炒葡人之家奪冠","createTime":"2020-12-12T00:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T03:26:31.000Z","uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64a1946dc80c8c84fe205bd12faf79c274e1af5d","tid":2321864,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:53:51.000Z","msg":"澳門盃甲組足球賽爭冠終極一戰，今晚7時賓菲加、澳科鄒北記分途出擊。 賓菲加憑射手哥爾斯轟入8球，教練兼隊長馬田斯球員生涯最後一役有士哥，賓菲加以23:1大炒葡人之家。<br />\n另一場，澳科鄒北記雖有迪亞高上演帽子戲法，以4球大勝士砵亭，但賓菲加仍以更佳得失球優勢，力壓鄒北記奪得冠軍。<br />\n#澳門盃 #甲組足球賽 #賓菲加 #澳科鄒北記 #葡人之家 #體育 #澳門日報 #澳日<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/131419062_1538797629644551_3337745997107126899_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=LNNcAUrDd4sAX-K9UFK&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-syd2-1.xx&amp;oh=0e6c75f299c7adc1b490af7119562144&amp;oe=5FFA375A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F131419062_1538797629644551_3337745997107126899_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DLNNcAUrDd4sAX-K9UFK%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-syd2-1.xx%26oh%3D0e6c75f299c7adc1b490af7119562144%26oe%3D5FFA375A&h=d7a4d64f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bba2687df33df4a4f54f9e67ddd12f7572d59a4","tid":2321864,"uid":109712,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:21:42.000Z","msg":"哩隊葡萄人之家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係包尾，對其他隊就精精神神，對榜首2隊可以輸0：15 / 1：23"},{"pid":"a29e03d4d82735b0f2b3138036362b8336ef083c","tid":2321864,"uid":39812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:29:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FSYbFlIsUwk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFSYbFlIsUwk&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmvhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=a9bf855a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FSYbFlIsUwk</a>"},{"pid":"5422c980de0a5fa9747096389a4c084fa208f2b5","tid":232